Package cwThree

This package contains the collection of classes to run the Elevator simulation, including creating customer objects with floor details.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Building
    This class asks the user for input to create a customer list and a building with a set number of floors.
    Customer
    This class creates a customer object with current floor and destination floor details, based on those values status of the object is also set such as whether current floor is 13 or whether they have reached their destination.
    Elevator
    This class creates an elevator with the methods to visit the building floor by floor picking and alighting customers.
    ElevatorTest
    Unit tests to assess functionality of the elevator system and customer.

Package cwThree Description

This package contains the collection of classes to run the Elevator simulation, including creating customer objects with floor details.
